toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104txx1665702829084.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/txx1665702829084.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/txx1665702829084.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"txx1665702829084\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                \n Define Polygons\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Draw and manage polygons for use within the map widget.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txx1665702829084__p_d9113e1_d9114e1_d9115e1\">Each area of the user's screen that is potentially sensitive to mouse action is called a polygon. Each polygon has a tag name and a tag title associated with it.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txx1665702829084__p_d9116e1_d9117e1_d9118e1\">The tag name is the value returned in the widget field when the tag is selected. The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">#Areas</span> field indicates the number of areas that have been defined for the tag.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txx1665702829084__p_d9119e1_d9120e1_d9121e1\">The tag's title is used as tool tip text and in the pop-up menu. The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Enable</span> field indicates whether the polygon is available to the user at run time.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Icons on the Define Polygons form</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"txx1665702829084__fig_w51ab1b5b7b3b7b1b1b1b1_w52ab1b5b7b3b7b1b1b1_w53ab1b5b7b3b7b1b1_w54ab1b5b7b3b7b1_w55ab1b5b7b3b7_w56ab1b5b7b3_w57ab1b5b7_w58ab1b5_w59ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Select polygon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_but_sel_off.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Selection mode</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"txx1665702829084__fig_w60ab1b5b7b3b7b3b1b1b1_w61ab1b5b7b3b7b3b1b1_w62ab1b5b7b3b7b3b1_w63ab1b5b7b3b7b3_w64ab1b5b7b3b7_w65ab1b5b7b3_w66ab1b5b7_w67ab1b5_w68ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Draw polygon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_but_draw_off.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Drawing mode</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"txx1665702829084__fig_w69ab1b5b7b3b7b5b1b1b1_w70ab1b5b7b3b7b5b1b1_w71ab1b5b7b3b7b5b1_w72ab1b5b7b3b7b5_w73ab1b5b7b3b7_w74ab1b5b7b3_w75ab1b5b7_w76ab1b5_w77ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Preview polygon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_but_none_off.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Preview polygon</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"txx1665702829084__fig_w78ab1b5b7b3b7b7b1b1b1_w79ab1b5b7b3b7b7b1b1_w80ab1b5b7b3b7b7b1_w81ab1b5b7b3b7b7_w82ab1b5b7b3b7_w83ab1b5b7b3_w84ab1b5b7_w85ab1b5_w86ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Delete polygon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_map_poly_del.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Delete polygon</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"txx1665702829084__fig_w87ab1b5b7b3b7b9b1b1b1_w88ab1b5b7b3b7b9b1b1_w89ab1b5b7b3b7b9b1_w90ab1b5b7b3b7b9_w91ab1b5b7b3b7_w92ab1b5b7b3_w93ab1b5b7_w94ab1b5_w95ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Separate polygon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_map_poly_sep.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Separate polygon</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"txx1665702829084__fig_w96ab1b5b7b3b7c11b1b1b1_w97ab1b5b7b3b7c11b1b1_w98ab1b5b7b3b7c11b1_w99ab1b5b7b3b7c11_w100ab1b5b7b3b7_w101ab1b5b7b3_w102ab1b5b7_w103ab1b5_w104ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Delete tag\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_map_tag_del.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txx1665702829084__table_d968e1_d969e1_d970e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Delete tag</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txx1665702829084__section_ukt_zgk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d869578e232\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"txx1665702829084__ul_z1x_zgk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"txx1665702829084__li_d4121e1_d4122e1_d4123e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ogk1665702644520.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ogk1665702644520.html\" title=\"Determines whether the polygon is enabled for the user to click. By default, the polygon is enabled.\">Enable/Disable Polygon (Disable)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"txx1665702829084__li_d4124e1_d4125e1_d4126e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yvd1665702644595.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yvd1665702644595.html\" title=\"Specify the name of the tag associated with a polygon or group of polygons.\">Tag Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"txx1665702829084__li_d4127e1_d4128e1_d4129e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"skt1665702644664.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/skt1665702644664.html\" title=\"The title of a map widget polygon is displayed on the pop-up menu of the widget, and as tool tip text if the Tool Tip property is selected.\">Tag Title</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"txx1665702829084__li_d4130e1_d4131e1_d4132e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eox1665702644734.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eox1665702644734.html\" title=\"Displays the number of areas, or polygons, that comprise this tag.\">#Areas</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532578\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532578\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Polygons Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Polygons Draw and manage polygons for use within the map widget. Each area of the user's screen that is potentially sensitive to mouse action is called a polygon. Each polygon has a tag name and a tag title associated with it. The tag name is the value returned in the widget field when the tag is selected. The #Areas field indicates the number of areas that have been defined for the tag. The tag's title is used as tool tip text and in the pop-up menu. The Enable field indicates whether the polygon is available to the user at run time. Table 1. Icons on the Define Polygons form Icon Meaning Selection mode Drawing mode Preview polygon Delete polygon Separate polygon Delete tag Fields Enable/Disable Polygon (Disable) Tag Name Tag Title #Areas Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}